data.description: PRICED TO SELL!! Two words: MULTIPLE. POTENTIAL!! This beautiful and charming single-family home is spacious and completely remodeled throughout! The main house is a true gem, boasting a spacious living area, the primary bedroom with an ensuite bathroom and walk in closet. It also has newer appliances, a new roof that's only one year old, and the AC is approximately 4 years old, The kitchen is immaculate and modern with white cabinetry and stone countertops to match. The garage was converted into another bedroom. Step outside and you'll be greeted by a tranquil and beautiful setting with an enclosed lanai ideal for lounging and relaxing. On what was previously the other 2 bedrooms of the main home, the owners have transformed it into an efficiency with it's own side door entrance completely separate from the main house with a kitchen/ living room combo, bedroom and bathroom. The possibilities are endless with this property, whether you simply need extra space for hobbies or storage. There's also a large outdoor shed that was doubling as a beauty shop with it's own water and AC capabilities. This property is truly one of a kind. Whether you're looking to for a multiple income property or simply enjoy the benefits of living close to major highways and universities, this property has it all. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Schedule a showing today and discover all that this property has to offer!
